items.name: SeerrBridge
items.description: SeerBridge automates movie torrent fetching by integrating Jellyseer/Overseer with DebridMediaManager. It listens to Discord movie requests and uses DMM / Real-Debrid for efficient downloads. With features like persistent browser sessions and queue management, it simplifies media handling. Future updates include TV show support and API integration.
